      "bookmarkId": "39206137_9_4625-4706",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4625-4706",
      "markText": "“日本军队是中国军队的磨刀石，中国共产党的军队就是在与日本作战中磨炼出来的，而在未来的内战中，拒绝与日本军队作战的国军主力，一定会被与日军作战的共军主力所击败。”",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39206137&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4625&rangeEnd=4706",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/458324f072563cf945855d5?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4625&rangeEnd=4706"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39206137_13_10120-10171",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "10120-10171",
      "markText": "这种气氛所留给我们的感受，是难以言传的，而只能去体验。它充满了迷人的魅力，并从此伴随着我们，日益增长。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39206137&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=10120&rangeEnd=10171",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/458324f072563cf945855d5?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=10120&rangeEnd=10171"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39206137_9_4050-4075",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4050-4075",
      "markText": "但毛泽东却是我见过的唯一一个能够统一全中国的人。”",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39206137&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4050&rangeEnd=4075",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/458324f072563cf945855d5?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4050&rangeEnd=4075"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39206137_9_2288-2360",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2288-2360",
      "markText": "中国共产党的领导人之所以毫无顾忌地透露出这些讯息，是因为他们无比坚定地相信，自己此刻正站立在历史转折点的紧要关头上，并能清晰地展望到前景和未来。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39206137&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2288&rangeEnd=2360",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/458324f072563cf945855d5?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2288&rangeEnd=2360"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39206137_14_1971-2010",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "1971-2010",
      "markText": "我们失去了和抗大校长林彪见面的机会。他在骑马时不小心跌落，严重骨折，正在养伤。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39206137&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1971&rangeEnd=2010",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/458324f072563cf945855d5?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1971&rangeEnd=2010"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39206137_14_7193-7239",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "7193-7239",
      "markText": "周恩来说，他愿意用英文进行采访，因为他需要练习。我们用英文开始了交谈。但很快就还是转为中文了",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39206137&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=7193&rangeEnd=7239",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/458324f072563cf945855d5?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=7193&rangeEnd=7239"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39206137_18_6714-6787",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "6714-6787",
      "markText": "在这两个党之外，中国其实没有其他政党真正存在。国民党的统治是建立在特权阶层的利益之上的；而共产党的统治，则是建立在工人阶级和农民阶级的利益之上的。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39206137&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=6714&rangeEnd=6787",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/458324f072563cf945855d5?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=6714&rangeEnd=6787"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39206137_20_2460-2496",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "2460-2496",
      "markText": "这一条件决定了，中国可以不用经过资本主义时代，而直接跨入社会主义的阶段。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39206137&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2460&rangeEnd=2496",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/458324f072563cf945855d5?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2460&rangeEnd=2496"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39206137_22_8812-8823",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "8812-8823",
      "markText": "那是延安最美好的岁月。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39206137&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=8812&rangeEnd=8823",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/458324f072563cf945855d5?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=8812&rangeEnd=8823"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39206137_6_1185-1271",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1185-1271",
      "markText": "他们之所以毫无顾忌地透露“具有完整情报”价值的“中国共产党的所有计划和意图”，是因他们“无比坚定地相信，自己此刻正站在历史转折点的紧要关头上，并能清晰地展望到前景和未来”。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39206137&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1185&rangeEnd=1271",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/458324f072563cf945855d5?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1185&rangeEnd=1271"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39206137_19_1078-1132",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "1078-1132",
      "markText": "南京看见，日本在上海开战，只是为了使他们对东北三省的占领合法化的一种手段，日本军队并没有占领沿海省份的打算；",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39206137&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1078&rangeEnd=1132",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/458324f072563cf945855d5?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1078&rangeEnd=1132"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39206137_19_2409-2451",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "2409-2451",
      "markText": "国民党认为，人民群众的抗日运动只会给日本人造成更多的借口，使日本更进一步地侵犯中国。",
